Scheme which provide grants to insulate homes and instal energy-saving
devices. The scheme, currently limited to those on income support, will be
extended to all pensioners and disabled people.
The cost of the package will be Pounds 416m in 1994-95, following the
imposition of VAT on domestic fuel at 8 per cent on April 1 1994. When the
